---
---

<!-- Ballot Access War -->
<section class="ballot-fight section-padding" id="ballot-fight">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label animate-in" style="text-align:center;display:block;" data-i18n="machine.fight_label">The Immediate Fight</span>
    <h2 class="section-title animate-in" style="text-align:center;" data-i18n="machine.fight_headline">The Ballot Access War</h2>

    <div class="fight-grid">
      <div class="fight-context animate-in">
        <p class="fight-text" data-i18n="machine.fight_p1">
          The machine is not just trying to outspend Byron. It is actively trying to keep him off the ballot entirely. Illinois election law is designed to punish independent candidates. While the machine's anointed candidate needed only 697 signatures to get on the ballot, Byron must collect exactly 10,816 valid signatures.
        </p>
        <p class="fight-text" data-i18n="machine.fight_p2">
          But it gets worse. The establishment will use bad-faith legal challenges to try and strike his petition signatures. Trained operatives will comb through every sheet, challenging every misspelled name, every address that is one digit off. To survive these challenges, the campaign must gather an overwhelming 40,000 to 50,000 signatures.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fight-numbers animate-in">
        <div class="fight-stat">
          <span class="fight-stat-number">697</span>
          <span class="fight-stat-label" data-i18n="machine.stat_machine">Signatures the machine's candidate needed</span>
        </div>
        <div class="fight-stat-vs">vs.</div>
        <div class="fight-stat fight-stat-movement">
          <span class="fight-stat-number">10,816</span>
          <span class="fight-stat-label" data-i18n="machine.stat_required">Signatures legally required of Byron</span>
        </div>
        <div class="fight-stat-vs">→</div>
        <div class="fight-stat fight-stat-target">
          <span class="fight-stat-number">50,000</span>
          <span class="fight-stat-label" data-i18n="machine.stat_needed">Signatures actually needed to survive legal challenges</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Framing -->
    <div class="fight-framing animate-in">
      <p class="fight-framing-text" data-i18n="machine.fight_framing">
        Signing this petition is not just a legal formality. It is an act of defiance against a system designed to suppress independent voices. Every signature is a direct challenge to the machine's grip on power.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Block -->
<section class="machine-cta-block">
  <div class="machine-cta-bg">
    <div class="machine-cta-pattern"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container machine-cta-content">
    <h2 class="machine-cta-headline animate-in" data-i18n="machine.cta_headline">Defy the Machine. Join the Movement.</h2>
    <div class="machine-cta-buttons animate-in">
      <a href="#petition" class="btn btn-orange btn-massive" data-i18n="machine.cta_petition">Join the Petition Blitz</a>
      <a href="https://secure.actblue.com/donate/byronfor04web/" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-i18n="machine.cta_donate">Fund the Insurgency</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ballot-fight {
    background: var(--cream);
    position: relative;
  }

  .fight-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .fight-text {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .fight-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Signature Stats */
  .fight-numbers {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border: 2px solid rgba(5, 173, 237, 0.1);
  }

  .fight-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .fight-stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--blue);
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .fight-stat-movement .fight-stat-number {
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .fight-stat-target .fight-stat-number {
    font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    color: var(--orange);
    text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(230, 136, 28, 0.2);
  }

  .fight-stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    display: block;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .fight-stat-vs {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  /* Framing */
  .fight-framing {
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--white);
    border-left: 5px solid var(--orange);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .fight-framing-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* CTA Block */
  .machine-cta-block {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .machine-cta-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue) 0%, var(--blue-deeper) 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .machine-cta-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0.04;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .machine-cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .machine-cta-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--cream);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .machine-cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .fight-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .fight-stat-target .fight-stat-number {
      font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    }

    .machine-cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .machine-cta-buttons .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
